{"ID":"20260605150641-i3l5nhn","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605150641-i3l5nhn","title":"2021年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605150655-54pnq3w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-54pnq3w","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"和陶归园田居（其一）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【1】"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-edtddyl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-edtddyl","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-b6w46oa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-b6w46oa","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"环州多白水，际海皆苍山。以彼无尽景，寓我有限年。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-mfbhkjq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-mfbhkjq","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东家著孔丘，西家著颜渊。市为不二价，农为不争田。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-g0lr46d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-g0lr46d","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"周公与管蔡"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【2】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，恨不茅三间。我饱一饭足，薇蕨补食前。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-cpfjdj9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-cpfjdj9","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门生馈薪米，救我厨无烟。斗酒与只鸡，酣歌饯华颠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【3】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-t9zjffc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-t9zjffc","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"禽鱼岂知道，我适物自闲。悠悠未必尔，聊乐我所然。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150655-i1b6wtg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150655-i1b6wtg","updated":"20260605150655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注释：【1】此诗作于苏轼被贬惠州时。一日苏轼游白水山佛迹岩，夜闻其子苏过诵陶渊明《归园田居》，于是作此诗。【2】周公与管蔡：西周初，管叔、蔡叔叛，周公率兵平叛。【3】华颠：头发花白。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150641-epjooxu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150641-epjooxu","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-tjjeapa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-tjjeapa","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．下列对诗句的分析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-ydsg5w4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-ydsg5w4","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．“环州多白水”四句写景，写惠州被群山环绕，幽僻而苍凉。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-u07vb32","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-u07vb32","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．“东家著孔丘”四句，写出了当地人的道德淳厚、民风纯朴。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-ns5ffiv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-ns5ffiv","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．“周公与管蔡”二句，设想彼此对立的人也会向往安居于此。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-imfwyrb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-imfwyrb","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．“我饱一饭足”二句，写生活虽穷困，但诗人仍能感到满足。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-7ko2cpm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-7ko2cpm","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．下列对这首诗的理解与赏析，正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-47v3fr0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-47v3fr0","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．本诗与陶诗都反映出诗人在远离官场之后，归隐田园的心情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-puzkgy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-puzkgy6","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．作者效仿陶渊明，在抒写田园生活时，表达了对劳作的热爱。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-9eiqm96","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-9eiqm96","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．陶诗原作除最后一句外通篇对仗，作者这首和陶诗也是如此。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-kam81c6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-kam81c6","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．本诗语言质朴而内涵丰富，正如作者评陶诗所言“质而实绮”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150705-fwwooqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150705-fwwooqp","updated":"20260605150705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．宋诗以理见长，苏轼这首诗也有此特点，请分析诗歌最后四句说出了怎样的道理。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150641-esb2x5d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150641-esb2x5d","updated":"20260605150721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605150721-996vh4e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150721-996vh4e","updated":"20260605150721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．A    13．D    14．①前两句侧重写人与自然的关系，说明心中有道，则能顺应自然，与自然、外物相融相亲。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150721-5vsphx9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150721-5vsphx9","updated":"20260605150721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②后两句侧重写诗人的超然态度，说明尽管外物未必和谐、美好，但内心的超脱也能使人自得其乐。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150641-xhu3r65","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605150641-xhu3r65","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-ri8ezm9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-ri8ezm9","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．本题考查学生分析诗句内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-ystoh86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-ystoh86","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“写惠州被群山环绕，幽僻而苍凉”错误，根据“以彼无尽景，寓我有限年”可知，作者认为此地风光无限，可以寄托自己的余生，并非“幽僻苍凉”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-68gtanr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-68gtanr","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-mmixnod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-mmixnod","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．本题考查学生理解赏析诗歌内容及艺术手法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-gshh98j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-gshh98j","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“都反映出诗人在远离官场之后，归隐田园的心情”错误，诗人并非远离官场，而是被贬惠州做官。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-snl98m3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-snl98m3","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“在抒写田园生活时，表达了对劳作的热爱”错误，本诗中作者并未表达对劳作的热爱，主要表达了闲适之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-wt0fw5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-wt0fw5p","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“陶诗原作除最后一句外通篇对仗，作者这首和陶诗也是如此”错误，原作中第二句“误落尘网中，一去三十年”也不对仗，第二句“以彼无尽景，寓我有限年”对仗，“门生馈薪米，救我厨无烟”“斗酒与只鸡，酣歌饯华颠”“禽鱼岂知道，我适物自闲”等句也不对仗，结构上并不一致。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-u87dve5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-u87dve5","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-3bdaiwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-3bdaiwb","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生理解诗句内容含义的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-stvk7uo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-stvk7uo","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“禽鱼岂知道，我适物自闲”两句意思是：鱼鸟哪里知道，只要我自己内心安闲，外物也自然安闲，这体现出人只要乐天安命，顺应自然，就不会为外在环境所苦，而感到闲适自在。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150735-hytvs1e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150735-hytvs1e","updated":"20260605150735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“悠悠未必尔，聊乐我所然”两句则是描述诗人的心境，“悠悠”指繁多的外物，“未必尔”即未必就是这样美好，但作者姑且能够以自己认同的事物感到快乐，即只要内心超脱，即使外物不顺心意，也能够自得其乐。"}]},{"ID":"20260605150641-gv1rfnh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605150641-gv1rfnh","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}